Thank you,
Zachary Roy

It is ok, someone did let me in and they were able to get someone that could translate on the call. They believed that EPP has a firewall that is blocking their SIEM tool connection from their GCP instance and that is not the case. They are going back to check on their rules and will report their findings after.

Thank you,
Zachary Roy
